long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Trackeet.co - Make Tracking Online Orders Easier!
Effortlessly track, organize and know exactly when your international orders will arrive, with Trackeet.

This Chrome Extension is made for helping our users to auto-scan their online orders, which later they will track them through Trackeet.
Currently, the tool supports Amazon/AliExpress/Ebay. When you are inside a valid order page at one of the mentioned websites-just open the extension and the auto-scan will be triggered.

For further details, please visit Trackeet.co
